('nigerian_professional', 'NIQS Probationary Exam', 'Measurement', 'Under SMM7, which rule covers the measurement of concrete works?', 'mcq', '["Rule 1", "Rule 2", "Rule 3", "Rule 4"]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Rule 3 covers concrete works measurement in SMM7.', 'medium', 2023),
