('nigerian_professional', 'NIQS Probationary Exam', 'Cost Planning', 'What is the elemental cost approach?', 'mcq', '["Pricing each item individually", "Allocating costs to building elements", "Using historical data only", "Applying a single rate per m2"]'::jsonb, 'B', 'The elemental cost approach allocates costs to building elements.', 'medium', 2023),
