('nigerian_professional', 'NIQS Probationary Exam', 'Cost Planning', 'What is the purpose of a cost limit?', 'mcq', '["To set the maximum expenditure", "To determine the minimum tender price", "To calculate the final account", "To estimate the contractor overhead"]'::jsonb, 'A', 'A cost limit sets the maximum expenditure the client will authorise.', 'easy', 2023),
