('nigerian_professional', 'NIQS Probationary Exam', 'BOQ', 'What is the primary function of a bill of quantities?', 'mcq', '["To provide a contract document", "To provide a common basis for tendering", "To set the final contract sum", "To calculate variations"]'::jsonb, 'B', 'The primary function of a BOQ is to provide a common basis for tendering.', 'easy', 2023),
