('nigerian_professional', 'NIQS Probationary Exam', 'BOQ', 'What is the difference between a provisional sum and a contingency?', 'mcq', '["There is no difference", "A provisional sum is for undefined work; a contingency is for unforeseen costs", "A contingency is for undefined work", "A provisional sum is always larger"]'::jsonb, 'B', 'A provisional sum is for work not yet defined; a contingency covers unforeseen costs.', 'medium', 2021),
